data.description: This 120 year old farm house sits on 11.2 acres and has 4 bedrooms with possible 5th and 3 bathrooms.  House has been renovated with modern conveniences; featuring sunroom, in-ground swimming pool, and pine wood cabinetry. Property sits on a private 2.5 acre stocked lake which is good for fishing and boating. Wooded acreage on property can be used for hunting, ATVs  and exploring. Horses or other live stock can be raised on this property that includes large wooden barn with stalls and a hay loft. Kitchen has quartz counter tops with center island and breakfast bar. Separate formal dining room that is open to living room.  Original hardwood floors throughout lower level Large master bedroom on lower lever with private bath and shower.  Main level laundry located with another 3/4 bathroom. Head upstairs there are 3 large bedrooms with another full bath.  A bonus bedroom/ office is located upstairs as well or can be converted to make a large master bedroom.
